MOVIE RECOMMENDATION
-> Content based recommendation system - focus on attributes of items. based on similarity b/w them
if user 1 likes to buy apple,banana,orange
if user 2 like to buy apple & orange
if user 3 like to buy apple
# this means apple & orange are so famous and we can recommend it to 4th user
same type of products are recommended in this system!


-> Collaborative filtering
#it uses user's behaviour
users similar to you if buy something then u may will also buy same thing